Key Match Events: Khama Billiat scored the winning goal for Zimbabwe in the 34th minute
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match took place in the Orlando Stadium in Gauteng, South Africa
Others: Zimbabwe held most of the ball during the first 10 minutes of the match but played the majority of the game inside their own half. Namibia came closest to scoring after Kennedy Amutenya hit the woodwork with a close-range header from a corner.
